content:
This is a component for adjustable notifications also known as toasts.

Import: import {Toaster, ToasterProvider, useToaster} from '@gravity-ui/uikit';

Category: feedback

Examples:
const {add} = useToaster(); add({name: 'my-toast', title: 'Success', theme: 'success'});
const {add} = useToaster(); add({name: 'error', title: 'Error occurred', theme: 'danger', content: 'Please try again.', isClosable: true});
<ToasterProvider><App /><ToasterComponent /></ToasterProvider>
